OL,3,CDefence company fined #800,000 over
OL,4,Cshooting error which left dad paralysed
OL,6,FA defence company has been fined
OL,7,F#800,000 after an employee was shot
OL,8,Fduring ammunition testing at a
OL,9,FMinistry of Defence (MoD) range in
OL,10,FWales.
OL,12,FA father-of-two was left paralysed
OL,13,Fbelow the shoulders after being shot
OL,14,Fby a 5.56mm bullet fired from a gun
OL,15,Ffrom 570 metres away, an incident
OL,16,Fwhich the Health and Safety Executive
OL,17,F(HSE) says "simple" steps could have
OL,18,Fprevented.
