OL,3,CDefence company fined #800,000 over
OL,4,Cshooting error which left dad paralysed
OL,6,FIt happened in March 2021 during a
OL,7,FNATO ammunition quality assurance
OL,8,Ftrial at the MoD Ranges in Pendine,
OL,9,FCarmarthenshire.
OL,11,FThe HSE said the role of the man, now
OL,12,F42, had been to check the impact of
OL,13,Fbullets on a metal target, and he was
OL,14,Fin front of the target when the bullet
OL,15,Fwas fired.
