OL,3,CDefence company fined #800,000 over
OL,4,Cshooting error which left dad paralysed
OL,6,FAn investigation by the HSE found
OL,7,Fdefence technology company QinetiQ
OL,8,FLimited had failed to adequately risk
OL,9,Fassess the trial activity, and did not
OL,10,Fhave adequate precautions in place to
OL,11,Fensure that nobody was near the target
OL,12,Fwhen the rounds were fired.
OL,14,FQinetiQ Limited, of Farnborough,
OL,15,FHampshire, pleaded guilty to breaching
OL,16,FSection 2(1) of the Health and Safety
OL,17,FAt Work etc Act 1974.
OL,19,FThe company was fined #800,000 and
OL,20,Fordered to pay #8,365 in costs at
OL,21,FLlanelli Magistrates' Court on 3 April.
