OL,4,Cshooting error which left dad paralysed
OL,6,FA QinetiQ spokesperson said: "We are
OL,7,Fdeeply saddened by the effect this
OL,8,Fincident has had on our colleague and
OL,9,Fhis family, who we continue to support.
OL,11,F"From the outset, as a company we have
OL,12,Facknowledged our profound regret,
OL,13,Faccepted responsibility and continue
OL,14,Fto demonstrate our commitment to
OL,15,Fprotecting our people; looking after
OL,16,Ftheir safety, health and wellbeing."
