OL,4,Cshooting error which left dad paralysed
OL,6,FHSE principal specialist inspector
OL,7,FStuart Charles said of the employee:
OL,8,F"His life and those of his wife and
OL,9,Ftwo children have been devastated by
OL,10,Fthe severe injuries he has suffered.
OL,12,F"Simple and inexpensive steps could
OL,13,Fhave been taken which would have
OL,14,Fprevented this incident.
OL,16,F"This case shows employers the
OL,17,Fimportance of continually assessing
OL,18,Fthe way they work and not just
OL,19,Faccepting historical practices."
